Class DW_Graph_Algo

java.lang.Object
api.DW_Graph_Algo
All Implemented Interfaces:
dw_graph_algorithms
public class DW_Graph_Algo
extends java.lang.Object
implements dw_graph_algorithms
DW_Graph_Algo implements dw_graph_algorithms represents a Directed (positive) Weighted Graph Theory Algorithms including: 0. clone(); (copy) 1. init(graph); 2. isConnected(); // strongly (all ordered pais connected) 3. double shortestPathDist(int src, int dest); 4. List shortestPath(int src, int dest); 5. Save(file); // JSON file 6. Load(file); // JSON file
